HEADWORD: Traducer
<hw>Tra*du"cer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
traduces; a slanderer; a calumniator.</def> <rj><au>Bp.
Hall.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who derives or deduces.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Fuller.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Traducian</ent>⟦br⟧
